data.name: tbTip.Text
data.value:
数据库表结构：
1.锚点表 CREATE TABLE "anchor_table" ( "id" INTEGER NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "time_stamp" INTEGER NOT NULL, "anchor_id" INTEGER NOT NULL, "is_enable" INTEGER, "x" INTEGER, "y" INTEGER, "z" INTEGER, "label" TEXT, "t0" INTEGER, "t1" INTEGER, "t2" INTEGER, "t3" INTEGER, "t4" INTEGER, "t5" INTEGER, "t6" INTEGER, "t7" INTEGER, "other" TEXT, UNIQUE ("id" ASC) ); x,y,z字段单位m，保存的是最开始锚点的位置和将来每次锚点的变动
2.原始信息表 CREATE TABLE "raw_table" ( "id" INTEGER NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "time_stamp" INTEGER NOT NULL, "raw_data" BLOB, "mid" BLOB, "mask" BLOB, "range0" BLOB, "range1" BLOB, "range2" BLOB, "range3" BLOB, "nranges" BLOB, "rseq" BLOB, "debug" BLOB, "at_a" BLOB, "other" TEXT, UNIQUE ("id" ASC) ); 保存的是定位标签上传到电脑的原始信息
3.目标点表 CREATE TABLE "tag_table" ( "id" INTEGER NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "time_stamp" INTEGER NOT NULL, "tag_id" INTEGER NOT NULL, "x" INTEGER, "y" INTEGER, "z" INTEGER, "r95" INTEGER, "anc0" INTEGER, "anc1" INTEGER, "anc2" INTEGER, "anc3" INTEGER, "other" TEXT, UNIQUE ("id" ASC) ); x,y,z字段单位cm，保存的是每次目标点的位置变动
